ersonal information from children under the age of 13 (or the applicable age in your region). Since we do not collect personal data, there is no risk of misuse of children\'s information.\n\n7. Data Security\n\nAs no personal data is collected or stored on external servers, there is no user data transmission or remote storage involved.\n\nWe are committed to maintaining a secure and safe user experience within the application.\n\n8. User Rights\n\nSince we do not collect or store personal information, there is no personal data to access, modify, or delete.\n\nUsers are free to uninstall the application at any time to remove locally stored data from their device.\n\n9. Changes to This Privacy Policy\n\nWe may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect improvements, feature changes, or legal requirements.\n\nAny updates will be reflected within the application along with the revised effective date.\n\n10. Contact Us\n\nIf you have any questions, concerns, or feedback regarding this Privacy Policy, you may contact us at:\n\nEmail: mygk001@gmail.com /Support WhatsApp Number 7068112460\n\nBy using GK GS Target Sarkari By SBAS, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.',
